title: Namas Te
description: Vegetarian restaurant and tea shop serving variety of imported teas, plus fresh fruit juices, afternoon sweets. Each day there is a set menu as well as fixed lunch beginning at noon (sometimes runs out fast, but there are other menu items such as veggie burger, eggplant, salads, fruit). Eclectic music, artwork, and outdoor garden. Location is a few blocks from Plaza San Pedro, just south of Almirante Grau on Zoilo Flores.
